Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ followed by \Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' for cases where activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that start with \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ out of all manuscripts
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Number of times \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ occurs before \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ that lead to a \SW-Checklist Completed\ status
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in relation to the total number of activities in the event log
Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ followed by \SW-AE Assign Reviewers\ within the variants
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Number of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ activities that precede a \SW-EIC Reject\ decision
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ activities that are part of manuscripts eventually accepted (followed by \SW-EIC Accept\)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ as the initial activity in the review process of scientific papers
Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ followed by any activity related to reviewer assignment or decision making (e.g., \SW-AE Assign Reviewers\, \SW-Reviewer Agreed\)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Number of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ activities that occur more than once within the same case
Metric: the sum of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ that are followed by a \Plagiarism Originality Report Completed\ within the same variant
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in manuscripts that undergo major revision (followed by \SW-EIC Major Revision\)
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in the top 3 most frequent starting activities in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all cases

Name: Number of variants that start with \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ and end with a decision (either \SW-EIC Accept\, \SW-EIC Major Revision\, \SW-EIC Minor Revision\, or \SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit\)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ followed by \SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days\ indicating urgency in the process
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Frequency of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ in relation to \SW-Checklist Completed\ to understand the efficiency of the checklist completion process
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' for cases where activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' occurs

Name: Percentage of \SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion\ that lead to a manuscript being withdrawn or rejected before review completion
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' out of all 'Manuscript is Withdrawn'
